  "prompt": "What percentage of Quora users ask and answer questions?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2021, Quora does not publicly disclose specific statistics regarding the percentage of users who ask questions versus those who provide answers. However, it's generally understood that a smaller percentage of users actively contribute by asking and answering questions, while a larger portion simply browses content. This is common across many Q&A platforms. For the most accurate and up-to-date statistics, I recommend checking Quora's official resources or user reports, as they may have released new information since then.",
